title: Dare To Be Creative iArchiver v1.2.5 Mac OSX-CFF
description:
Another application for Mac users. This one comes from publisher with interesting name ?Dare To Be Creative?. Dare you to be creative? Dare you? Ha, punk? Lol. :D Ok, back on track. This application will help you to extract-compress-convert most popular compression formats known today, such as ZIP, RAR, 7-ZIP and more.

Description:

Pack
You need to send large files to a customer? You want to distribute your files as DMGs? Create DMG, Zip, 7-zip and many other formats quickly and easily with iArchiver.

Extract
You can?t open that email attachment? No problem, iArchiver opens Zip, DMG, RAR, StuffIt (.sit), HQX and many more common and uncommon formats

Convert
